OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright spells are
OL,6,Fpossible on Tuesday, though much of
OL,7,Fthe day looks cloudy. Some showers are
OL,8,Flikely in the north and west at first,
OL,9,Fthese becoming heavy and more
OL,10,Fwidespread into the afternoon, with a
OL,11,Fchance of thunder.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FEarly showers will die out
OL,14,Fduring the evening to leave a largely
OL,15,Fdry night. Some clear intervals,
OL,16,Falthough low cloud, and some mist and
OL,17,Ffog patches are likely to form.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
