OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fwill soon lift to leave a fine day
OL,7,Facross the region. It will be dry,
OL,8,Falthough with fairly cloudy skies
OL,9,Fpersisting sunshine will be hazy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FOvernight rain should have cleared by
OL,13,FThursday morning, with plenty of
OL,14,Fsunshine developing during the day.
OL,15,FSouthern areas look mostly settled
OL,16,Fthereafter, though some patchy rain
OL,17,Fcould develop further north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
